commit message: Revert bump in version code.  It doesn't need to be v15+ instead of v14+

Fix nonRelease builds

If not releasing set android.signingConfigs to null

Add JavaDoc generation to build.

Now JavaDocs will be generated with each build.  This gives a quick
reference to casual viewers and developers on the project

If private.creds file is missing do not fail.

If private.creds are supplied then perform a release build. If not
then perform a debug build.
Add more comments to the build.gradle members

Travis build.

Attempt to fix build on TravisCI.  Seems we are missing the android-22 sdk version.

Merge pull request #28 from JBirdVegas/travis

Fix Travis build.
